edu.stanford.cs.unittest

Class UnitTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.cs.unittest.UnitTest

  • public class UnitTest
extends java.lang.Object
    The UnitTest class supplies several static methods that are useful in writing unit tests. Clients may also extend the UnitTest class to avoid having to write the UnitTest prefix with every test method.
